current_pf_12.description: in similar format as ZIPload, this is the power factor of the phase 12 constant current portion of load

impedance_pf_12.description: in similar format as ZIPload, this is the power factor of the phase 12 constant impedance portion of load

power_fraction_1.description: this is the constant power fraction of base power on phase 1

current_fraction_1.description: this is the constant current fraction of base power on phase 1

impedance_fraction_1.description: this is the constant impedance fraction of base power on phase 1

power_fraction_2.description: this is the constant power fraction of base power on phase 2

current_fraction_2.description: this is the constant current fraction of base power on phase 2

impedance_fraction_2.description: this is the constant impedance fraction of base power on phase 2

power_fraction_12.description: this is the constant power fraction of base power on phase 12

current_fraction_12.description: this is the constant current fraction of base power on phase 12

impedance_fraction_12.description: this is the constant impedance fraction of base power on phase 12

group.description: the group ID to output data for (all links if empty)

filename.description: the file to dump the current data into

runtime.description: the time to check voltage data

runcount.description: the number of times the file has been written to

rated_motor_speed.description: Rated speed of the VFD in RPM. Default = 1800 RPM

desired_motor_speed.description: Desired speed of the VFD In ROM. Default = 1800 RPM (max)

rated_output_voltage.description: Line to Line Voltage - VFD Rated voltage. Default to TO node nominal_voltage

rated_horse_power.description: Rated Horse Power of the VFD. Default = 75 HP

nominal_output_frequency.description: Nominal VFD output frequency. Default = 60 Hz

desired_output_frequency.description: VFD desired output frequency based on the desired RPM

efficiency.description: Current VFD efficiency based on the load/VFD output Horsepower

stable_time.description: Time taken by the VFD to reach desired frequency (based on RPM). Default = 1.45 seconds

tilt_angle.description: tilt angle of pole from the centerline

install_year.description: the year of pole was installed

repair_time.description: typical repair time after pole failure

pole_stress.description: ratio of actual stress to critical stress

pole_stress_polynomial_a.description: constant a of the pole stress polynomial function

pole_stress_polynomial_b.description: constant b of the pole stress polynomial function

pole_stress_polynomial_c.description: constant c of the pole stress polynomial function

susceptibility.description: susceptibility of pole to wind stress (derivative of pole stress w.r.t wind speed)

total_moment.description: the total moment on the pole

resisting_moment.description: the resisting moment on the pole

pole_moment_nowind.description: the moment of the pole without wind

equipment_weight.description: the moment of the equipment weight

equipment_moment_nowind.description: the moment of the equipment without wind

wire_weight.description: wire moment due to conductor weight

wire_moment_x.description: wire moment in x-axis due to tension and wind load

wire_moment_y.description: wire moment in y-axis due to tension and wind load

equipment_moment_x.description: equipment moment in x-axis due to wind load

equipment_moment_y.description: equipment moment in y-axis due to wind load

wire_tension.description: wire moment due to conductor tension

pole_type.description: material from which pole is made

pole_length.description: total length of pole (including underground portion)

ground_diameter.description: diameter of pole at ground level

height.description: height above ground at which equipment is mounted

offset.description: distance from pole centerline at which equipment is mounted

direction.description: direction from pole centerline at which equipment is mounted
